-- LeBron James Announcement Special on ESPN Receives 7.3 Overnight Rating
-- Jay Beberman
-- 2010-07-09T15:23:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/lebron-james-announcement-special-on-espn-receives-7-3-overnight-rating.html

          
          
             LeBron James’s special “The
Decision” on Walt Disney Co.’s ESPN network received a 7.3
overnight rating.  
 Cleveland had a 26 rating and Miami a 12.8, ESPN spokesman
Mark Mandel said in an e-mail.  
 James, the National Basketball Association’s two-time Most
Valuable Player, announced that he was leaving the Cleveland
Cavaliers for the Miami Heat.  
          
          


  


        